Mai sayar da kayayyaki Sainsbury's na shirin karfafa matsayinsa a kasuwar kyawawan kayayyaki da kayayyakin kwalliya a Burtaniya
Sainsbury ta ɗauki Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams, suna ba da yankuna na kayan kwalliya a cikin salon shagon duniya, tare da ƙwararrun mataimakan tallace-tallace.
A wani bangare na karfafa matsayin a kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya mai darajar fam biliyan 2.8 da ke ci gaba da bunkasa, duk da cewa tallace-tallace na kayan gida da na kayan kwalliya ba su daidaita ba, za a gwada manyan sassan kayan kwalliya a shaguna 11 a kasar kuma za a haɗa su a cikin shaguna da yawa a shekara mai zuwa, idan sun kasance masu nasara.
Zuba jari a masana'antar kyakkyawa ya zo ne a yayin da manyan kantuna ke neman hanyar amfani da sararin da aka saba amfani da shi don talabijin, microwaves da kayayyakin gida.
Wakilan dillalin Sainsbury sun ce za a ninka adadin kayayyakin kwalliyar da suke samarwa zuwa 3,000, wanda zai hada da, a karon farko, kayayyaki kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw.
Kasuwancin da ke akwai, kamar L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees, za su sami ƙarin sarari, tare da wuraren da aka yiwa alama, kamar na Boots.
Har ila yau, babban kanti yana sake ƙaddamar da jerin kayan kwalliyarsa, Boutique, wanda ke nufin cewa yawancin samfuran suna ga masu cin ganyayyaki, buƙata da ke ƙaruwa tsakanin matasa masu siye.
Bugu da kari, za a saka kayayyakin kantin sayar da kayan kwalliyar Faransa The Fragrance Shop a shagunan Sainsbury guda biyu domin gwaji, na farko da aka bude a makon da ya gabata a Croydon, kudancin London, na biyu kuma a Selly Oak, Birmingham, a karshen wannan shekarar.
Sayayya ta yanar gizo da kuma son sayan ƙananan abinci a kowace rana daga kantin sayar da abinci mafi kusa yana nufin cewa manyan kantuna suna buƙatar nemo sabbin hanyoyin da za su sa mutane su ziyarce su.
Mike Coupe, babban jami'in kamfanin sayar da kayayyaki na Sainsbury's, ya ce, kantunan za su kara kama da kantunan duniya, yayin da manyan kantunan sayar da kayayyaki ke kokarin fuskantar manyan kantunan sayar da kayayyaki, Aldi da Lidl, wadanda ke samar da ayyuka da kayayyakin da ba na abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ya hada da kayayyakin Argos a daruruwan shagunan da Habitats tun lokacin da ya sayi duka sarkar biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, wanda ke nufin cewa ya sami karuwar tallace-tallace na abinci da kuma karuwar riba.
Taƙaddamar da kantin sayar da kayayyaki na kantin sayar da kayayyaki da kayan kwalliya ya gaza.
Sainsbury's ya yi ƙoƙari ya haɗu da Boots a farkon 2000s, amma tattaunawar ta ƙare bayan rikici game da yadda ake raba kudaden shiga na shagunan Boots a cikin manyan kantunansa.
An tsara sabon dabarar ne bayan da Sainsbury ya sayar da kasuwancinsa na kantin magani wanda ya hada da kantuna 281 ga Celesio, wanda ke da sarkar Lloyds Pharmacy, na fam miliyan 125 shekaru uku da suka gabata.
Wannan yana nufin Lloyds zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin shirin, yana ƙara manyan samfuran samfuran fata, gami da La Roche-Posay da Vichy, a cikin shaguna huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na kamfanin sayar da kayayyaki na Sainsbury's ya ce: "Mun sauya fasalin wurarenmu na kayan kwalliya don inganta yanayin mu ga abokan cinikinmu.
Mun kuma saka hannun jari wajen koyar da ƙwararrun abokan aikinmu, waɗanda za su kasance a shirye su ba ku shawara.
Jerin samfuranmu na iya daidaitawa ga kowane buƙata, kuma kyakkyawan yanayi da wurare masu dacewa suna mai da mu wuri mai ban mamaki don siyan kayan kwalliya, yana kawo sauyi kan tsohuwar hanyar siyayya.
Peter Jones ya yi fushi bayan Holly Willoughby ta janye daga kwangilar fam miliyan 11
Jarumin shirin "Dragons' Den" Peter Jones ya yi fushi bayan da mai gabatar da shirin "Dragons' Den" Holly Willoughby ta janye daga kwangilarsa ta fam miliyan 11 da kamfanin sa na salon rayuwa domin mayar da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyar da ta kulla da Marks & Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokacin shiga cikin aikin su na Truly, wanda ya haɗa da kayan haɗi da kayan gida.
An kwatanta kamfanin ma'auratan da alamar Goop, mallakar Gwyneth Paltrow.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning mai shekaru 37 ta sanar a shafinta na Instagram cewa za ta janye.
Holly Willoughby ta fusata Peter Jones, wanda ke cikin shirin Dragons Den, ta janye a lokacin ƙarshe daga kasuwancin su na sabis na rayuwa don mai da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyar ta da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Rahotanni sun ce Jones ta yi fushi lokacin da daya daga cikin shahararrun 'yan wasan talabijin ta yarda a ranar Talata, a lokacin wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali a hedkwatar kasuwancinta a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin kwangilolinta, masu darajar har zuwa fam miliyan 1.5, ba sa ba ta damar sadaukar da kanta ga alamarsu ta Truly, wanda ya hada da kayan haɗi da kayan gida.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop kuma kusan ya ninka dukiyar Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta ya kai fam miliyan 11.
Bayan Willoughby, mai shekaru 37, ya sanar a shafin Instagram cewa zai bar kwangilarsa na Truly, Jones ya bar Burtaniya don neman mafaka a daya daga cikin gidajen hutunsa.
Sanarwar da aka samu: "Gaskiya ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da Holly ta fi so.
Wannan zai zama makomar ta na tsawon shekaru ashirin.
Yanke shawarar janyewa ya girgiza kowa.
Babu wanda ya yarda da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, lokacin da aka kusan kaddamar da shi.
Akwai wani babban sito cike da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow da suke shirye su sayar.
Masana sun yi imanin cewa janyewar mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, wanda ke cikin fitattun taurari a Burtaniya, na iya haifar da asarar miliyoyin ga kamfanin, sakamakon saka hannun jari a cikin kayayyaki kamar su matashin kai da kyandir, tufafi da kayan gida, da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkirin ƙaddamarwa.
Zai iya zama ƙarshen abokantaka na dogon lokaci.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar 'ya'ya uku, da Dan Baldwin, mijinta, sun kasance abokai na shekaru goma tare da Jones da matarsa, Tara Capp.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016, kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga matsayin darektan a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata suna hutu tare, kuma Jones yana da kashi 40% na hannun jari a kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby zai zama jakadan M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na ITV.
Wani majiya da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a daren jiya, "Ba ma son mu yi magana game da harkokin kasuwancinsa".
