Idan aka yi la'akari da girgizar ƙasa da Indonesia ke fuskanta a kai a kai, abin mamaki ne cewa ƙasar ba ta da shiri sosai don fushin yanayi.
Ko da yake an gina wuraren kwantar da tsunami a Aceh, ba a saba samunsu a wasu yankunan bakin teku ba.
Kamar dai rashin isharar tsunami a Palu, duk da cewa an bayar da gargadi, na iya taimakawa wajen rasa rayuka.
