Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sanarwar da 'yan jarida suka bayar game da dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A lokaci guda, hargitsi na siyasa ya ci gaba, inda tashoshin talabijin suka katse shirin su na yau da kullum na ranar Juma'a domin wani labari na karshe: yarjejeniyar da aka yi tsakanin Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona da FBI don gudanar da bincike kan zargin na tsawon mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa hukumar cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade yayin da yake cikin maye kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
