A cewar Nielsen, mutane sama da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli zaman da aka yi a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya kirga matsakaicin kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a nan take aka samu adadin sauran gidajen rediyon da suka watsa shi ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yana da matsala wajen ganin mutane suna kallon fim daga ofishinsa.
