Sha'awa ta kasance a kan babban matakin bayan sauraron.
Flake ne ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin Jam'iyyar ta Moderate ya fitar da sanarwa cewa zai kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, CNN da CBS sun yi fim da shi a safiyar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zanga ke ihu a kansa yayin da yake kokarin hawa cikin wani lif a wani zaman kwamitin shari'a.
