Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu, da dama daga cikinsu ta hanyar manyan raƙuman ruwa da suka yi ta fadowa daga rairayin bakin teku, lokacin da wata girgizar ƙasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami suka afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, hukumomi sun ce a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane ne suka taru a ranar Juma'a a wani bikin rairayin bakin teku a garin Palu, lokacin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon kafa shida suka mamaye rairayin bakin teku da yamma, inda mutane suka yi ta nitsewa suna lalata duk abin da ke gabansu.
An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 bayan tsunami.
"Lokacin da aka yi barazanar tsunami a jiya, mutane suna kan ayyukan su a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu ba nan da nan, kuma sun zama wadanda suka kamu da cutar", in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar kula da matsalar BNPB, a wani taron manema labarai a Jakarta.
Tsunami ya kwashe motoci, bishiyoyi, gidaje, ya buge duk abin da ke kan tudu, Nugroho ya ce, ya kara da cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya zuwa teku da saurin kilomita 800 a awa daya kafin ya kai gabar teku.
Ya kara da cewa wasu mutane sun hau bishiyoyi domin tserewa tsunami kuma sun tsira.
