Turai ta yi nasara 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai ta fara ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup da gagarumar nasara bayan kammala wasannin kwallon kwando da na hudu a ranar Asabar da ci gaba 10-6 a gaban Amurka.
Abokan haɗin gwiwa na Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci harin tare da nasara biyu a gaban Tiger Woods mai jinkiri, wanda ya haɓaka ƙimar su zuwa yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke ƙoƙarin sake lashe kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye 'yan wasan Amurka waɗanda suka yi kuskure da yawa a wasan kwallon kafa na safe kuma suka ci wasan ta hanyar 3 zuwa 1.
Amurka ta yi tsayayya sosai a wasan hudu, inda ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage ragamar ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas a wasanni 12 da suka yi a ranar Lahadi domin ta ci kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon ɗan wasan Turai na farko da ya ci maki huɗu a jere, kuma tare da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da Molliwood bayan babban karshen mako, sune na biyu da suka ci maki huɗu a wasannin buɗewa huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kwando, sun yi nasara sosai a kan Woods da Bryson Dechambeau, 'yar wasan Amurka mai ƙwazo, da ci 5-4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasannin biyu na Asabar, ya sami wasu 'yan wasa na ɗan lokaci, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a cikin kwallaye da kwallaye, bakwai daga cikinsu sun kasance masu nasara.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a lokacin zaman wasannin hudu na safe, ya dawo tare da abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu kuma suka doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, matsayi na ɗaya da uku a duniya, da ci 2-1 .
Duk da haka, Turai ba ta samu damar tafiya ba tare da wata matsala ba a wannan rana mai kyau da sanyi a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun zama abin da ya sa a kan gaba a gasar, inda suka ci maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun yi nasara da ci 2-1 a wasan da suka yi da 'yan Spain Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan kwallon kwando, sannan suka dawo daga baya suka doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy da ci 4-3 a wasan kwallon kwando, bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup ne wata kungiya ta iya murmurewa ta hanyar kasa da maki hudu a wasannin tseren, kodayake, saboda su ne masu riƙe da kofin yanzu, 'yan wasan Furyk suna buƙatar kawai a daidaita su.
Amma bayan sun kasance a matsayi na biyu na kwana biyu, wani hari a ranar Lahadi ba zai yiwu ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce babu wata dama ta kawar da makaman ta kai tsaye muddin babu amincewa
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa tsawaita takunkumin zai kara zurfafa rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu kasar ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta ba a cikin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na majalisar cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu mahimmanci don tabbatar da kyakkyawan imani" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin nukiliya da gwajin makami mai linzami, rushe wurin gwajin nukiliya da kuma alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasaha.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani martani na Amurka ba", in ji shi.
Idan ba za mu iya amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za mu iya amincewa da ƙarfinmu na tsaro na ƙasa ba, kuma a irin waɗannan yanayi ba za mu iya kawar da makamanmu ba.
Duk da cewa Ri ya sake maimaita takunkumin da aka saba yi wa Koriya ta Arewa game da kin amincewa da Washington ta yi wa tsarin "shan-shan" na kawar da makaman nukiliya, wanda ya ce za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada idan ta dauki matakai a hankali, kalamansa sun kasance masu ma'ana saboda bai yi watsi da kawar da makaman nukiliya ba kai tsaye kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a wani taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da kuma shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin samun ci gaba wajen 'yanta yankin Koriya ta Koriya ta 'yan ta'adda, yayin da Trump ya bayar da tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi a kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950 zuwa 1953, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara ba da makaman nukiliya.
Bugu da kari, Washington ta ki amsa buƙatun sassauta takunkumin ƙasashen duniya mai tsanani da aka kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan zaɓin "ƙetare makaman nukiliya da farko" kuma tana ƙara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma tana adawa da "yankewar yakin", in ji Ri.
"Halin da ake ciki cewa takunkumi zai iya durkusar da mu, ruɗu ne da mutanen da ba su san mu ba kawai suke da shi.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da takunkumi yana kara sa mu cikin rashin amincewa.
Ri bai ambaci shirin wani taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana a kai a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya yi nuni da ganawa uku tsakanin Kim da Moon Jae-in, shugaban Koriya ta Kudu, a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: Idan da an tattauna batun kawar da makaman nukiliya da Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, da ba a kai ga wannan matsin lamba ba.
Ko da a wannan yanayin, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bambam da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya bayyana wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa ne a kai makamai masu linzami kan Amurka daga Koriya ta Arewa bayan da "Mista muguwar Shugaba" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami" a cikin aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda ya yi barazanar "hallaka Koriya ta Arewa" a bara, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa na fara aikin kawar da makaman, amma ya ce aikin ya fara ne kawai kuma takunkumi zai ci gaba har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da aka tsara domin wannan, ya kara da cewa: Ba kome ba ko ya dauki shekaru biyu ko uku ko watanni biyar.
China da Rasha sun ce ya kamata Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta biya Pyongyang diyyar matakin da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: Aikata takunkumin Majalisar Tsaro dole ne ya ci gaba da karfi ba tare da katsewa ba har sai mun cimma cikakkiyar, karshe da kuma tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya.
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da tsaurara takunkumin da aka kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa tun daga shekarar 2006, a wani yunkuri na toshe kudaden da ake samu don shirin nukiliya da makamai masu linzami na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a cikin gangaren babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma daga baya ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ziyarar ta karshe ba ta da sakamako mai kyau.
Lokacin da ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli, ya ce an samu ci gaba, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i kadan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi tir da cewa ya yi 'barazanar' yan bindiga.
A wani taro da Moon ya yi a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe tashar harin makami mai linzami da kuma wani makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakai masu dacewa".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore kuma yana son daidaita dangantakarsa da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard suna koyar da darussa game da yadda za a samu isasshen hutu.
Wani sabon darasi a Harvard a wannan shekara yana karfafa wa dalibai su samu karin bacci, a kokarin da suke yi na yaki da al'adun "macho" da ke sa su shiga zaman karatu na dare, tare da samun karin kuzari da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'o'i mafiya daraja a duniya sau da yawa ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, shi ne ya kirkiro wannan darasi, wanda ake ganin shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ya samu kwarin gwiwa wajen tsara wannan darasi bayan ya gabatar da wani darasi game da tasirin rashin bacci akan iyawar mutum na koyo.
A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa aka gaya mini wannan a shekarar da ta gabata?"
Ta gaya min cewa ba a taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci ba, abin da ya ba ni mamaki, "in ji shi a cikin jaridar The Telegraph.
Darasi, wanda aka gabatar a karon farko a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai muhimman abubuwan da suka shafi yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa wajen inganta aikin ilimi da na wasanni da kuma jin daɗin rayuwa.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma babban daraktan ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan ta gano cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci a lokacin mako.
Darasi na awa ɗaya zai iya ƙunsar ayyuka masu ma'ana.
Wani sashe na nuna hoton ɗakin kwana, kuma ɗalibai za su iya danna kofuna na kofi, labule, wando, da littattafai don a gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin bacci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin shirin bacci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mutane yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar da ke ɗauke da hotunan hotunan, tana ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da tsarin aikinsu na yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa ba za mu iya canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da hakkin su sani, kamar yadda kowa yake da hakkin ya san abin da shan sigari ke yi wa lafiyarsu", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar da ke sa dalibai su yi alfahari da cewa sun yi karatu dare da rana har yanzu tana nan, in ji shi, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba ga dalibai sun mayar da rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai karuwa.
Ya ce samun isasshen bacci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama makamin da dalibai suke amfani da shi wajen magance damuwa da gajiya da kuma damuwa, har ma da guje wa samun karin nauyi, domin rashin bacci yana sa kwakwalwa ta yi tunanin cewa jiki yana fama da yunwa, wanda hakan ke sa dalibai su ji kamar suna fama da yunwa a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, wani dalibi dan shekara 19 a California da ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da kuma ilimin lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen kirkirar wannan darasi bayan ya halarci daya daga cikin darussansa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya sa ya yi wahayi zuwa ga dukan ɗalibai.
Mataki na gaba, ya yi fata, shi ne a bukaci dukkan daliban da suka kammala karatun digiri su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga wannan ma'aikata inda gasar ke da tsananin gaske.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci ɗalibai su saita ƙararrawa don su san lokacin barci da lokacin farkawa, kuma su san illolin da "hasken shuɗi" da ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da LEDs, wanda zai iya lalata saurin circadian kuma ya haifar da wahala lokacin da suke ƙoƙarin yin bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: raga da Menga ta ci wa tawagar Gerrard
Rangers suna fama da wani yanayi na damuwa a kan tafiya saboda bugun da Dolly Menga ta yi ya sa Steven Gerrard ya yi rashin nasara a wasan da aka yi da Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta nemi nasarar farko a kan tafiya tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da suka yi a watan Fabrairu a kan St. Johnstone, amma Gary Holt ya gudanar da Gerrard ta biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, wanda ya sa Rangers ta samu maki takwas a baya da Hearts, shugabannin jagorancin Ladbrokes Premiership.
Menga ya ci kwallo da minti bakwai kafin hutun kuma 'yan wasan Rangers da ba su da kwarin gwiwa ba sun yi kasa-kasa da kara.
Rangers sun sauka zuwa matsayi na shida a cikin jerin, yayin da Livingston suka hau zuwa matsayi na uku, a baya Hibernian, ta hanyar raga guda.
Kuma Rangers na iya fuskantar wasu matsaloli, saboda alkalin wasa Calum Spence ya bukaci a kula da shi saboda ciwon kai bayan da wani abu ya yi kama da an jefa shi daga filin wasan da magoya bayan tawagar suka ziyarta.
Gerrard ya maye gurbin 'yan wasa takwas daga wasan da ya yi nasara da sauƙi a kan Ayr a wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya yi amfani da 'yan wasa 11 na Livingstone da suka yi nasara a wasan da suka yi da Hearts a makon da ya gabata, kuma yana da dalilin yin alfahari da yadda tawagarsa ta kwantar da hankulan abokan hamayyarsa a wasan.
Ko da yake Rangers sun fi kowa, Livingston ya fi amfani da kwallaye da suke da su.
Ya kamata ya ci kwallo ne da minti biyu bayan fara wasan, lokacin da bugun farko na Menga ya tura Scott Pittman zuwa ƙofar da Allan McGregor ya kare, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya rasa babbar dama.
Keaghan Jacobs ya yi wani babban harbi na kyauta wanda ya samu kyaftin din Craig Halkett, amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya tura shi a kan bar.
Rangers sun dauki ragamar wasan, amma sun nuna cewa suna da kwarin gwiwa fiye da yadda suke ganin ya dace a wasan.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi imanin cewa ya kamata a ba shi fanareti lokacin da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless a minti na goma sha biyar na wasan, amma mai wasan Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da bukatar dan wasan Colombia.
Rangers sun samu kwallaye biyu a raga a farkon wasan, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, bai damu da Lassana Coulibaly ba ko kuma Ovie Ejaria.
Ko da yake kwallo da Livingstone suka ci a minti na 34 bai yi daidai da yanayin wasan ba, babu wanda zai iya musanta cewa an cancanci hakan, ko da kuwa saboda ƙoƙarin da aka yi.
Sai dai kuma, Rangers sun kasa hana Jacobs yin zurfin tsakiya.
Scott Arfield bai yi wani abu ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya tura kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai nutsuwa kuma ya ba da shi ga Menga, wanda ya kammala da bugun jini.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu, lokacin da ya canza Ryan Kent zuwa Coulibaly; wannan yunkurin ya kusan ba da gudummawa nan da nan, lokacin da matsanancin ya sanya Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya fita daga cikin bututun don toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi zuwa ainihin irin wasan da ya fi so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna tsallake cibiyar cibiyar.
Holt zai iya karawa da sauran 'yan wasan, amma McGregor ya iya toshe Jacobs, sannan Lithgow ya tura shi a kan ƙofar.
Glenn Middleton, dan wasan Rangers, ya nemi a yi masa bugun jini a karshen wasan, lokacin da ya buga Jacobs amma kuma Thomson bai yarda ba.
Almanah: wanda ya ƙirƙira na'urar lissafin Geiger
Kuma yanzu, shafi na Almanahinmu na safiyar Lahadi: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce (kuma ana ci gaba da kirgawa...), ranar da aka haifi, a Jamus, masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger.
Geiger ya haɓaka hanyar ganowa da auna radiyo, wanda ya haifar da ƙirƙirar na'urar da aka sani da Geiger counter.
Na'urar da ta kasance da muhimmanci ga kimiyya tun daga lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama mahimmanci ga al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda ya faru a cikin fim din "The Bells of San Coronado" (1950), wanda ya nuna Roy Rogers da Dale Evans a matsayin 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na' yan wasan kwaikwayo tare da rashin amincewa da kimiyya:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan kuma?"
Rogers:  Wannan na'urar Geiger ne, da ake amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo, kamar su uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan kwalkwali, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ɗin rediyo ke yi a cikin ma'adanai.
Evans:  Ee, akwai yawan bugun jini!
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kaɗan kafin ya cika shekara 63.
