HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin masu kamuwa da cutar
China ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen kasar da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar Sin, in ji jami'ai.
An samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, ba kamar yadda aka saba ba.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yaɗu da sauri a wasu wurare a ƙasar Sin ta wurin ƙarin jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma duk da haka, a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da dubu ɗari.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana ganin nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Saboda tsattsauran ra'ayin da ake da shi a ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da mazaje za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan da ake yadawa sun samo asali ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin irin wannan dangantaka.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun maganin cutar HIV ga kowa, a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya ba da bayanan ga 'yan majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican, tana magana ne game da "karya mai hatsari" da kuma "ka'idar makirci".
'Yar majalisa Maxine Waters ta yi tir da zargin da ake yi cewa wani memba na tawagarta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yar Democrat din daga Los Angeles ta yi ikirarin cewa masu sharhi da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan tsattsauran ra'ayi ne ke tuhumar.
Waters ya ce a cikin wani sakon Twitter.
Bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adiresoshin da lambobin waya na sirri na sanata Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu na Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a intanet a ranar Talata, wanda ba a san ko wane ne ba a kan Capitol Hill a lokacin da ake sauraron karar da aka yi a majalisar dattawa kan zargin da ake yi wa Brett Kavanaugh na yin lalata da 'yan mata da aka nada a matsayin mai shari'a a kotun koli.
Wannan bayanan ya faru ne jim kadan bayan da 'yan majalisar su uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen aika saƙon an haɗa shi da ofishin Waters kuma sun ba da bayanin ga memba na ƙungiyar Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Waɗannan zarge-zargen ba su da tushe, ƙarya ce, karya ce kwarai", in ji Waters.
Mambobin tawagar, wanda aka lalata sunansa, bayanansa da amincinsa sakamakon wadannan zarge-zargen karya, ba su da alhakin wannan bayanan.
Waɗannan zarge-zargen da ba su da tushe ba ƙarya ne, ƙarya ce ta gaske.
Bayanan Waters sun fuskanci suka a kan layi jim kadan bayan da aka yi su, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da halin da ya dace ya zama dan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Bai kamata ya zama mai ƙin yarda ba.
Bai kamata su yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumar ba.
Dole ne ya kasance mai nutsuwa da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya bayyana cewa yana kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da na mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda 'yan Democrat suka soki, wanda suka ce ya yi kama da ɗan fushi a lokacin sauraron sa a ranar Talata.
Omar Navarro, dan jam'iyyar Republican da ke takarar Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, shi ma ya yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Mai muhimmanci, idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi.
A cikin sanarwar ta, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya gargadi  hukumomi da hukumomin da suka dace game da waɗannan zarge-zargen.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu laifin", ta ci gaba, "kuma za su amsa a gaban doka don duk ayyukan da suka yi da suka lalata kuma suka yi wa kowane memba na tawagar barazana".
Johnny English ya sake yin fim: fim din da ke nuna cewa 'yan leken asiri ne, wanda Rowan Atkinson ke taka rawa
Ya zama al'ada a nemi ma'anar da ke tattare da Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya, amma wannan ba ya shafi sabon fim ɗin daga jerin wasan kwaikwayo na fim ɗin da ke nuna Johnny English, jerin da ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake dawowa cikin 2011 tare da Johnny English ya dawo.
Shin wannan abin dariya na yadda muke da ban mamaki zai iya zama sabon damar fitar da kaya ga al'umma?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English, ɗan leƙen asiri mai ƙyalli da idanu masu tsinkaye da fuskar roba, an sabunta shi a karo na biyu don ya ɓata komai. Sunan halayensa yana nufin, da farko, cewa yana da babban abin ban dariya ga masu kallo na fina-finai a ƙasashen da ba su magana da Ingilishi ba.
Shi ne, ba shakka, mai ba da labari na sirri wanda, duk da sonsa na alatu da ban sha'awa, yana da ɗan Clouseau, ɗan Mr. Bean da kuma ƙusa na irin wanda ya ba da gudummawa a cikin waƙa ta Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London.
Halin ya dogara ne akan mai binciken da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki wanda ba shi da ƙasa wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard, wanda ya bar rikici a bayansa.
Wannan sabon abu na JE yana da wani abu mai kyau ko biyu.
Na ji daɗi lokacin da Johnny English ya kusanci wani helikafta sanye da makamai na zamanin da kuma ƙyallen rotor ɗin ya yi wa kwalkwali na ɗan sauƙi.
An nuna baiwar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki, amma abin dariya yana da rauni kuma, baƙon abu, ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman saboda fina-finai masu mahimmanci, kamar na 007 ko Mission Impossible, suna ba da tabbacin lokacin wasan kwaikwayo.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a gare ni, abubuwan ban dariya na Johnny English ba su da basira da basira kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim din fim din da yake wasa da Bean.
Kamar yadda aka saba, abin da aka saba da shi shi ne cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin gidan yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya kuma ya bayyana sunayen jami'an Birtaniya da ke karkashin kasa, har ma da takaici ga mai aikin, wani rawar da Kevin Eldon bai taka ba.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga wani firaminista mai girman kai da ke cikin hari, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga mummunan rikici saboda raguwar shaharar siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin duk abin da ta iya tare da halayenta na kama da Theresa May, amma rubutun ba ya ba ta damar haskakawa.
Masu ba ta shawara a harkar leken asiri sun sanar da ita cewa an lalata dukkan 'yan leken asiri da ke aiki, don haka dole ne ta kunna wani wakili a cikin ajiya.
Wannan shi ne Johnny English da kansa, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malamin makarantar sakandare, amma kuma yana koyar da yadda ake zama ɗan leƙen asiri. Ga wasu kyawawan abubuwa, domin English yana gudanar da makarantar leƙen asiri ta School of Rock.
An dawo da Turanci zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa, sannan ya sake haɗuwa da abokin aikinsa na dā, Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga.
Bough yanzu ya auri wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa, mai matukar farin ciki da kuma daraja, rawar da Vicki Pepperdine ta yi amfani da ita.
Saboda haka, waɗannan Batman da Robin na rikice-rikice a cikin Sirrin Sirrin Mai Girma sun dawo cikin aiki, suna fuskantar kyakkyawar femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ya fada cikin wata masifar da ta shafi wani mai karfin gaske na masana'antar fasaha wanda ke ikirarin cewa zai iya magance matsalar IT ta Burtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara tafiya a cikin balaguron balaguro: suna yin ado a matsayin masu hidimar, suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa, suna haifar da hargitsi lokacin da suka shiga cikin jirgin ruwan Volta, sannan Turanci ya haifar da rashin tsari a cikin tsari mai tsabta lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da saitin tabarau na gaskiya don sanin abubuwan da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Wannan fim na ƙarshe yana da ƙwazo sosai, amma duk da cewa fim ɗin yana da kyau da kuma launuka, yana kama da shirin talabijin na yara.
Wannan fim ɗin bai da kyau sosai.
