Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa wajen " toshe " kayayyakin da Rasha ke fitarwa, in ji sakataren cikin gida
Washington na iya, "idan ya zama dole", ta yi amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha zuwa wasu kasuwanni, ciki har da yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shigar Rasha Syria musamman inda take aiki a kan gayyatar da gwamnatin ta yi, wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su yi aiki a matsayin masu sayar da wutar lantarki, kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai da kuma kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
