"Lokaci ya yi da mace za ta je Washington ta gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma wannan yana bukatar mace mai karfi", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai ko zan tsaya takara a zaben shugaban kasa".
Warren ya kuma yi magana game da shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron garin, yana cewa ya "jawo kasar cikin hanyar da ba ta dace ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump sosai da kuma Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya nada shi a matsayin babban alkalin kotun.
A wani sakon Twitter da ya wallafa ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "a kullum muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a kada kuri'a".
