Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun kalubalanci sabon tsarin neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia na goyon bayan takaddama ta shari'a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda ke kokarin tserewa daga tashin hankali ko tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar sun gabatar da takardar neman izinin neman mafaka a ranar Juma'a a Washington, D.C., NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da Kungiyar 'Yancin Jama'ar Amurka ta kaddamar a watan Agusta ba game da dokar tarayya.
Ta ce abokin aikinta da 'ya'yanta masu aikata laifi, 'yan kungiyar 'yan bindiga, sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An kama ta a Texas.
Lauyan da aka nada na jihar da ke wakiltar Grace ya bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, wadanda suka samar da masu neman mafaka da yawa a Amurka, a matsayin kasashe da ke fuskantar matsalar gangs da tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar Amurka ta neman mafaka ta soke shawarar da Majalisar 'Yan Gudun Hijira ta yanke a 2014 da ta bai wa baƙi marasa tushe damar neman mafaka da ke neman tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Babban lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa.
"Dokar tarayya ta ce dole ne a yi la'akari da duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan iyakancewa ya sabawa wannan ka'ida", in ji amicus curiae.
Bugu da ƙari, lauyoyi sun yi jayayya a cikin takardar cewa manufar hana baƙi shiga tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa suna iya zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su samar da aikin da ake buƙata.
Jeff Sessions, babban lauyan Amurka, a watan Yuni ya umarci alƙalan 'yan gudun hijirar da su daina bai wa wadanda ke neman mafaka mafaka daga cin zarafin 'yan bindiga da kuma tashin hankali.
"Ana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke barin ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron nuna bambanci saboda launin fata, addini, ƙasa, ko ƙungiyar zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a ranar 11 ga Yuni, lokacin da ya sanar da manufar.
Matsayin mafaka bai taba zama na magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a duniya ba, ko da kuwa duk matsalolin da suka fi tsanani.
