Ba mu da lokacin da za mu tsere.
Na shiga cikin rugujewar bangon, na yi imani, "in ji Harris ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press, inda ya kara da cewa danginsa suna cikin gari domin bikin aure.
