Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da cin zarafin 'yan jaridar ta
Mako guda bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yabon amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labarai na Amurka wajen rarraba kayan yaɗa labarai.
A ranar Laraba ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da karin kudin da kasar Sin ta biya jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wani zargi da kasar Sin ta musanta.
Zargin da ake yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin shiga cikin zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa Reuters cewa sabon mataki ne a wani yunkuri na kara matsa lamba a kan China.
Ko da yake al'ada ce gwamnatocin kasashen waje su buga tallace-tallace da ke tallata kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin kasuwanci da ke ci gaba, wanda ya kunshi yawan karin haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
Harajin da China ta saka a matsayin fansa a farkon yakin cinikayya an kirkireshi ne domin ya shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana a China da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
A wani labari da aka wallafa a ranar Lahadi a cikin Des Moines Register, Branstad ya rubuta cewa China "tana ci gaba da wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"A lokacin da suke yada farfaganda ta hanyar buga talla a cikin Des Moines Register, gwamnatin China ba ta bin al'adar 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da kuma 'yancin latsa labarai da ake so a Amurka", in ji Branstad.
"A gefe guda, a kan kantin sayar da jaridu a kan titi a nan birnin Beijing, za ku ga 'yan muryoyin masu adawa kaɗan, kuma ba za ku ga ainihin tunani game da ra'ayoyin da suka bambanta da 'yan kasar Sin ke da shi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, "daya daga cikin manyan jaridu a kasar Sin ta ki buga" labarin, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da masu jefa kuri'a mata kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara saboda batun Kavanaugh, manazarta sun gargadi
Kamar yadda yawancin manyan 'yan Republican ke goyon bayan da kuma kare Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli, daga zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a sami adawa, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
Tashin hankali da wannan abin kunya ya haifar ya kasance mai ƙarfi, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican da suka tattauna game da shi a fili suna shirin ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a manta da irin wannan martani ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana da shakku cewa matakin karshe na Sanata Jeff Flake game da binciken FBI zai kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da gobe ba, kuma ba za su manta da Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kungiyar masu ci gaba a kasar, a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jaridar Washington, D.C. ta ruwaito.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga sun yi ihu "Bari Nuwamba ya zo!" yayin da suke zanga-zanga a zauren majalisar dattawa lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zabi ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Democrat zai kasance mai matukar farin ciki da kuma motsawa", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa mai nuna rashin son kai ga shafin yanar gizon.
Mutane sun ce sun riga sun yi girma sosai, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma za su iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin yankunan karkara da kuma matasa masu zabe, tsakanin shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda, duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a.
Tun kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili, inda ya bayyana zargin cin zarafin da aka yi wa wanda ya zaɓa a kotun koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya samun koma baya idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da shi.
"Wannan ya zama abin da ya zama matsala ga 'yan Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko kuma ko za a tabbatar da Kavanaugh, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da wannan lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, daraktan Priorities USA, wani rukuni na goyon bayan zabe na Democrat, ga tashar labarai.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun rarrabu a kan abin da ya kamata su gaskata bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh: 'yan kadan sun fi gaskata da na biyun.
Wani sabon bincike da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun yi imanin ko kuma sun yi imanin cewa shaidar Ford ta kasance gaskiya, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imanin ko kuma sun yi imanin cewa shaidar Kavanaugh gaskiya ce.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin 100 sun ce Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya, wataƙila ko kuma tabbas, yayin da kashi 30 cikin 100 suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan Flake ya fara, FBI na binciken zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma akalla wani mutum, Deborah Ramirez, jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade sa'ad da take 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta yi ikirarin cewa wanda aka nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun kasar ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a gabanta yayin da suka halarci wani biki yayin da suke daliban Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar intanet domin ya yi gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfanin da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da mashahurin masanin fasaha, Inrupt ya yi, kamfani ne da ke kan Solid, dandalin Berners-Lee mai budewa.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma wanda ke da damar samun damar bayanin.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi waƙar cewa manufar da ke bayan Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Yanzu dole ne mu yi shi", ya yi magana game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar shafin yanar gizon su na sirri ko PODs.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobi, shirye-shirye, kalandarku, ɗakunan kiɗa, ko wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna nan a cikin burauzar yanar gizo, duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da wannan rumbun adana bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken iko kan wanda zai iya samun damar irin wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar ita ce Inrupt ta samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basira don samar da Solid ga kowa.
A yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, ƙungiyar masu haɓaka da ke aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su yi magana da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da sauyi gaba daya lokacin da tsarin kasuwancin su ya lalace gaba daya.
Ba ma neman izininsu.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a Medium ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabuwar intanet a kan Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka-tsakin Intanet.
Ko bayan ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, da Web Foundation da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan zamanin na Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
