Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji kasa saboda jima'i
Tom Daley mai ruwa da na'ura mai ruwa da na'ura mai ruwa ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa ya fi kowa saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya sa ya yi nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci ba har sai da ya isa makaranta cewa "ba kowa bane kamar ni".
A lokacin da aka gayyace shi a shirin farko na shirin Desert Island Discs da Lauren Laverne ta gabatar a Radio 4, ya ce yana magana ne game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi domin ya ba wa wasu "bege".
Dan wasan ya kuma ce lokacin da ya zama uba, ya daina damuwa da wasannin Olympics.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da shirin na yau da kullum, za ta yi rashin lafiya na 'yan watanni.
Da aka gayyace shi zuwa fitowar farko da Laverne ta gabatar, Daley ya ce lokacin da yake yaro ya ji ƙasa ga sauran mutane saboda ba a yarda da shi ba daga zamantakewar jama'a don son yara maza da mata.
Ya ce, "Har zuwa yanzu, wannan jin kasa da kuma jin banbanci, su ne ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi da juriya don samun nasara".
Yana son ya tabbatar da cewa shi wani ne, in ji shi, don kada ya bata wa kowa rai idan suka gano cewa shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Wanda ya lashe lambobin tagulla biyu a wasannin Olympics ya zama sanannen mai goyon bayan kamfen na LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanar a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su yanke hukunci game da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yanke shawarar yin magana ne saboda yana jin ya yi sa'a da ya sami 'yanci ya rayu ba tare da wata sanarwa ba, kuma saboda yana son ya ba wa wasu bege.
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi mamakin yadda ya yi soyayya da wani mutum, dan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black.
Daley ta auri dan wasan fim mai lashe lambar yabo ta Oscar a bara, wanda ya girme ta da shekaru 20, amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da ka sha irin wannan wahalar a irin wannan ƙuruciya - ta shiga gasar Olympics ta farko lokacin da take 'yar shekara 14, kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga ciwon daji bayan shekara uku - " ya ce, "yana da wuya a sami wani da shekarunsa ya sha irin wannan farin ciki da rashin farin ciki.
A watan Yuni, sun haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce hakan ya canja ra'ayinsa.
"Idan aka tambaye ni a bara, zan so in lashe lambar zinare", in ji shi.
Akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare a gasar Olympics muhimmanci.
Robbie ne lambar zinare ta gasar Olympics.
An sa wa ɗansa sunan mahaifinsa, Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 bayan an gano shi da cutar kansa ta kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya so shi ne ya san ko sun samu tikiti zuwa gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London domin yana son ya kasance na farko.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, ba za ka iya zama na farko ba, Baba", in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma bayan ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu, sai na yarda cewa ba shi da nasara", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya yi gasa a wasannin Olympics na 2012 kuma ya lashe lambar tagulla.
"Na san wannan shine burin rayuwata, tsalle a gaban masu sauraron kasarmu a wasannin Olympics, babu wata jin dadi fiye da wannan", in ji shi.
Wannan kuma ya sa ya yi waƙar da ya zaɓa, Proud by Heather Small, waƙar da ta ƙarfafa shi kafin wasannin Olympics kuma har yanzu tana motsa shi.
An gabatar da shirin Desert Island Discs a tashar BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15.
