Muna da wasanni 12 masu muhimmanci a gobe kuma muna so mu fara da gagarumar nasara, kamar a Brookline, kamar a Medina.
Idan aka samu wannan rashin motsi a hanya guda, sai a matsa matsi sosai a kan matuka a tsakiya.
