Amurka ta yi la'akari da hukunta kasar El Salvador saboda yarjejeniyar da ta yi da China, amma daga baya ta yi watsi da hakan
'Yan diplomasiyar sun lura cewa Jamhuriyar Dominica da Panama sun riga sun amince da Beijing, tare da ɗan adawa daga Washington.
Trump ya yi wata ganawa da shugaban Jamhuriyar Panama Juan Carlos Varela a watan Yunin 2017 kuma ya mallaki wani otal a Panama har sai abokansa suka kori kungiyar shugabannin kungiyar Trump.
Jami'an ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka sun yanke shawarar dawo da shugabannin jakadun Amurka a El Salvador, Jamhuriyar Dominica da Panama sakamakon 'yan kwanan nan da suka yanke shawarar daina amincewa da Taiwan', in ji Heather Nauert, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar a cikin wata sanarwa a farkon wannan watan.
Amma an yi la'akari da takunkumin ne kawai a kan kasar El Salvador, wadda ta samu tallafin Amurka na kimanin dala miliyan 140 a shekarar 2017, ciki har da kula da miyagun kwayoyi, ci gaba da tallafin tattalin arziki.
Takunkumin da aka gabatar, wanda ya hada da rage tallafin kudi da takunkumin biza, zai zama mai zafi ga kasar na Amurka ta tsakiya da kuma yawan rashin aikin yi da aikata laifuka a ciki.
Yayin da tarurrukan cikin gida suka ci gaba, jami'an Arewacin Amurka da na tsakiya sun dage wani babban taron da ya mayar da hankali kan tsaro da wadata ta tattalin arziki, domin ci gaba da irin taron da aka yi a bara, wanda ake ganin mataki ne na gaba wajen hana bakin haure zuwa Amurka.
Amma a tsakiyar watan Satumba, jami'an gwamnatin sun bayyana cewa suna son ci gaba da taron, a zahiri sun kawo karshen duk wani bincike kan takunkumin da aka kafa a kan El Salvador.
