An bayyana cewa Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar kekuna a kan titin West Side na Lower Manhattan, yana harba masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don a iya yanke masa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara na bukatar su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi kisan da gangan ga wadanda aka kashe da kuma cewa ya yi sanadin raunin jiki, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar a kotun kudancin New York.
Dukkanin masu gabatar da kara na iya samun hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotun.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da suka hada da tuhume-tuhume takwas na kisan kai da ya taimaka wa masu aikata laifuka, wanda ake amfani da shi a matsayin babban laifi a shari'ar masu aikata laifuka, da kuma na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
