Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo rauni, wahala da asara ga iyalan da abokan wadannan mutane: Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
