Abokan hulda sun jaddada cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin kulla yarjejeniya da Brussels, ba tare da la'akari da sakamakon ba, kuma za ta tilasta wa masu shakkar Turai da jam'iyyar Labour su zabi tsakanin tayin ta da kuma Haos.
Bone ya ce a taron 'yan Brexit na Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son ya yi watsi da shirin Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa Farage ya kasance cikin ƙungiyar kuma a ba shi alhakin da ke tattare da tattaunawar tare da Brussels.
"Da a ce shi ne ke tafiyar da al'amura, da ba ma cikin Tarayyar Turai", in ji shi.
