Andrea Jenkyns, memba na Conservative Party mai goyon bayan Brexit, ita ma tana wajen zanga-zangar kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai: "Ina so in ce kawai: Madam Firayim Minista, ku saurari muryoyin mutane.
