Dundee Stars sun ci gaba da cin nasara 5-3 a kan Giants na Belfast
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun biya diyya a wasan da suka yi a ranar Juma'a, inda suka ci Belfast Giants a wasan dawowarsu na ranar Asabar, da ci 5-3 a Dundee.
Giants sun yi nasara da kwallaye biyu, tare da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita wasan kafin Dwyer ya mayar da Giants a gaban 'yan wasan.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wasan da Dundee suka ci kafin kwallo biyu da Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci ya tabbatar da nasara.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da 'yan wasan Adam Keefe suka sha kaye a gasar Elite League a bana, inda suka yi nasara da Dundee da ci 2-1 a ranar Juma'a.
