"Muna ganin adadin zai karu, saboda yawancin wadanda suka mutu suna cikin lalacewar kuma ba mu da damar shiga da yawa daga cikinsu", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Tawayen da suka kai tsawon kafa shida sun lalata garin Palu, inda aka yi jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiyar 'ya'ya mai shekara 35, ta shaida wa Sky News cewa: "Kowane minti, wani motar asibiti na kawo mutane.
Yana da kusan ba zai yiwu ba a sami ruwan sha.
An yi wa dukan kantunan sayar da kayayyaki fashi.
Jan Gelfand, daraktan kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa ta Red Cross ta Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa ta Indonesia tana gaggauta kai taimako ga wadanda suka tsira, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu a wurin ba.
Tuni dai abin ya zama bala'i, amma zai iya ƙara muni.
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya ce wa sojojin kasar: Ina rokon ku da ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala dukkan ayyukan kwashe mutane.
"Shin kuna shirye?" in ji CNN.
A farkon wannan shekarar, an yi wata girgizar kasa a Lombok a Indonesia, inda mutane fiye da 550 suka mutu.
Hadarin jirgin sama a Micronesia: Air Niugini ta ce yanzu mutum daya ya bace bayan jirgin ya fadi cikin tafkin
Kamfanin jirgin da ke da jirgin da ya yi hatsari a wani tafkin tekun Pacific a Micronesia ya ce yanzu mutum daya ya bace, bayan da ya ce a baya dukkan fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun tsere daga jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa cewa wani matafiyi namiji ya bace tun ranar Asabar da yamma.
Ta kuma ce tana kokarin gano mutumin tare da hukumomin gari da asibitoci da masu bincike.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa ba da sauri ga buƙatun ƙarin bayani game da fasinja, kamar shekaru ko ƙasa.
An yi amfani da jiragen ruwa na mazauna garin don ceto sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya yi karo da ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin sama na tsibirin Chuuk.
A ranar Juma'a, hukumomi sun ce an kwashe mutane bakwai zuwa asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar kuma dukkansu suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Har yanzu ba a san abin da ya haddasa hatsarin ba kuma ba a san ainihin yadda abubuwan suka faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da rundunar sojin ruwan Amurka sun ce jirgin ya rasa filin saukarsa kuma ya shiga wani tafki kusa da shi.
Wasu shaidu sun ce jirgin ya wuce gefen filin jirgin.
Wani fasinja dan Amurka mai suna Bill Jaynes ya bayyana cewa jirgin ya kai kasa da nisa daga kasa.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu fasinjoji sun tsallaka ruwan da ya kai ga kwanyar jirgin kuma suka isa wajen fitowar jirgin da ke nitsewa.
Ya kuma ce mataimakan jirgin sun firgita kuma suna ihu kuma ya ji rauni a kai.
Rundunar sojin ruwan Amurka ta ce masu aikin jirgin ruwa da ke aiki a kusa da wurin da ake gyara wani tashar jirgin ruwa sun zo su taimaka, suna amfani da jirgin ruwa mai taya don kai mutane bakin tekun kafin jirgin ya nutse zuwa zurfin mita 30 a karkashin ruwa.
A cewar bayanan da ke cikin cibiyar sadarwa ta tsaro na sufuri, mutane 111 ne suka mutu a hatsarin jiragen sama da aka yi rajista a PNG a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata, amma babu wani daga cikinsu da ya shafi jirgin Air Niugini.
