A ranar Asabar, mai gabatar da kara ya kammala jawabinsa game da sake fara shari'ar wani mutum da ake zargi da kona wata mata a Mississippi a 2014.
Paul Rowlett, wani manazarci a Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amirka, ya ba da shaida na sa'o'i da yawa a matsayin gwani a shaidar bincike.
Ya bayyana wa alƙalan yadda ya yi amfani da bayanan wayar salula don ya haɗa ayyukan Quinton Tellis, mai shekara 29, da kuma na wanda ya kashe, Jessica Chambers, mai shekara 19, a daren da ta mutu.
Rowlett ta ce ta samu bayanan wurin da ake kira Tellis daga wayoyin salula da dama da suka nuna cewa tana tare da Chambers a daren da aka kashe ta, wannan ya sabawa kalaman da ta yi a baya, a cewar jaridar Clarion Ledger.
A lokacin da bayanan suka nuna cewa wayar salula ta kasance tare da Chambers lokacin da ya ce yana tare da abokinsa, Michael Sanford, 'yan sanda sun tafi su yi magana da Sanford.
An kira Sanford a kan kujera kuma ya shaida cewa ba ya cikin gari a wannan rana.
Lokacin da masu gabatar da kara suka tambayi Tellis ko ya faɗi gaskiya lokacin da ya ce yana cikin motar Sanford a wannan daren, Sanford ya ce ya yi ƙarya, saboda motar ta tana Nashville.
Wani rashin daidaito shi ne cewa Tellis ya ce ya san Chambers kusan makonni biyu lokacin da ta mutu.
Bidiyo na wayar salula sun nuna cewa sun san juna a makon da ya gabata.
Rowlett ta ce jim kadan bayan mutuwar Chambers, Tellis ya goge sakonnin rubutu, kira, da bayanan tuntuɓar Chambers daga wayarsa.
"Ya goge ta daga rayuwarsa", in ji Hale.
A lokacin da aka tsara, masu kare za su fara jawabin su na ƙarshe a ranar Lahadi.
